{
  "id": "69e88da11c7090a1acf55fb9",
  "title": "情報源は何か？",
  "created": 1776848290,
  "updated": 1776849505,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e88da11c7090a1acf55fb9",
      "text": "情報源は何か？",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776848290
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da200000000005f2260",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776848290
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da400000000005f2266",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848292,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da200000000005f2262",
      "text": " [情報源]は俺だ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da200000000005f2263",
      "text": " 「[情報源としての井戸端]」民として貢献しようとするとどんな動きになるのか？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da200000000005f2264",
      "text": " 今日の、これ見てます系は普通にへーってなる、ちょうどいい情報",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88da200000000005f2265",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848290,
      "updated": 1776848290
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd50000000000a5a832",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848342,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a829",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849440,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82a",
      "text": " 情報源について考えていた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82b",
      "text": " \t\tこの辺: [2025/09/08#68be6fa00000000000b72974]、[2025/09/08#68be6f150000000000b7296d]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82c",
      "text": " \t井戸端に頼りすぎるのはよくない（井戸端が、というより情報源が少なすぎること自体の弊害がでかそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82d",
      "text": " \tニュースやSNSを想像するが、それ以外もある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82e",
      "text": " \t\tたとえば[チームみらい]の、生きた人間の営みを読むことも情報収集になるだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a82f",
      "text": " \t\tたぶんパートナーや（リアルで会う）友人がいたらそれだけで足りそうな気もするが、僕はそうじゃない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776849440
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a830",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776848340
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dd30000000000a5a831",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848340,
      "updated": 1776848340
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ecb",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776848380
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e020000000000015eeb",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848386,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ecd",
      "text": " 情報源、自分の場合なんだろう？全部挙げられる気がしないけど書き出してみるかなあ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ece",
      "text": " \t[ラジオ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ecf",
      "text": " \t\t基本流しっぱで、たまにニュースが入る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed0",
      "text": " \t\t[日曜天国]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed1",
      "text": " \t\t\t月食はこれで知った",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed2",
      "text": " \tお客さんとのちょっとした雑談",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed3",
      "text": " \tイベントや勉強会に顔を出して雑談",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed4",
      "text": " \t自分が主宰しているオフラインでのおしゃべりの会",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed5",
      "text": " \t入ってる[Cosense.icon][複数人Project]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed6",
      "text": " \t\tパブリックなのは井戸端だけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed7",
      "text": " \t\t他は7, 8くらい分野別でprivate、それぞれに4–20人くらい人がいる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed8",
      "text": " \tRSSフィード",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ed9",
      "text": " \t人文書",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015eda",
      "text": " \t\t古典でよくわからん箇所は、生成AIに投げて解説させる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015edb",
      "text": " \t配偶者",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015edc",
      "text": " \t本屋に平積みの新刊本",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015edd",
      "text": " \t図書館の雑誌コーナーの表紙だけザッと眺める",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ede",
      "text": " \t[ホッテントリ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015edf",
      "text": " \t[XTwitter]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee0",
      "text": " \t\t現代思想系アカウントのタイムライン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee1",
      "text": " \t\tボドゲ系アカウントのタイムライン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee2",
      "text": " \tFacebookのタイムライン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee3",
      "text": " \t学会のシンポジウム",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee4",
      "text": " \t\t一昨日の[2025/09/07#68bee1e50000000000acfec3]なんかは、ネットでも本でも取得できない情報だった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee5",
      "text": " \t旅行系YouTuberチャンネル",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee6",
      "text": " \t\t地方のお店や土産物、観光地情報など",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee7",
      "text": " \t[TVer]で定期で見てる番組",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee8",
      "text": " \t天気や災害系はスマホの通知",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015ee9",
      "text": " \t政治理論の読書会に4, 5年毎月行っていてそれも貴重な情報源の場だったが、最近不定期開催になって行かなくなっちゃった（なので自分で分野を変えて、自分で主催することにして軽く情報交換の場として代替している）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88dfc0000000000015eea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848380,
      "updated": 1776848380
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79b4",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776848427
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2d00000000002f79bf",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848430,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79b6",
      "text": "時事ネタの情報源は通勤時のラジオ、昼飯食べながら見るNHKの12時のニュース、気まぐれに見るYahooニュースのトピックス一覧を眺める",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79b7",
      "text": "\t[https://news.yahoo.co.jp/topics トピックス一覧 - Yahoo!ニュース]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79b8",
      "text": " トピックス一覧は興味あるニュースも興味ないニュースもどうでもいいニュースも見たくないニュースもざっくりと出て良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79b9",
      "text": " [X.icon]は全く触ってないので井戸端経由で得てる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79ba",
      "text": " ゲーム関連のニュースはまとめサイトをたまに見る程度で、次のゲーム何買うかなとなって探し出す感じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79bb",
      "text": " 緊急の時事ネタはスマホに入れている[NHKニュース・防災]経由",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79bc",
      "text": " [回覧雑誌]のことを忘れていた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79bd",
      "text": " \t月刊誌とか季刊誌で大体７冊か",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e2b00000000002f79be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848427,
      "updated": 1776848427
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e45",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776848466
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e46",
      "text": "[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e47",
      "text": "\t情報源",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e48",
      "text": "\t\t本",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e49",
      "text": "\t\t[X.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4a",
      "text": "\t\t[Cosense.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4b",
      "text": "\t\t[YouTube.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4c",
      "text": "\t\t友だち、家族",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4d",
      "text": "\t\t[地方紙]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4e",
      "text": "\t\t\t家族で取っており食卓においてあるので目に入る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e4f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tあ～これあるな[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e50",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこの観点、なるほど[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e51",
      "text": "\t\tテレビ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e52",
      "text": "\t\t\t点いてたら見ちゃう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e53",
      "text": "\t\tチャッピー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e54",
      "text": "\t\t[Spotify.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e55",
      "text": "\t\t本屋",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e56",
      "text": "\t\t\t最近この本がよく並んでるなとか、この本が表に置いてあるのめずらしいなという雰囲気の情報を得ている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e57",
      "text": "\t\t\t図書館もこれかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776848466
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e520000000000d91e59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848466,
      "updated": 1776848466
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca799",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776848494
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79a",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849439
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79b",
      "text": "情報源の話気になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79c",
      "text": "\t会社",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79d",
      "text": "\tSNS",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79e",
      "text": "\tRSS",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca79f",
      "text": "\tDiscord [inajob川]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a0",
      "text": "\tスマートフォンのホーム画面のGoogleのおすすめ記事",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a1",
      "text": "\t[はてなブックマーク]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a2",
      "text": "\t妻・娘",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a3",
      "text": "\t井戸端",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a4",
      "text": "\tポッドキャスト",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a5",
      "text": "\t偏りがひどい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88e6e0000000000fca7a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848494,
      "updated": 1776848494
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc159",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776848749
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15a",
      "text": "[kana.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15b",
      "text": "情報源かあ。ものによるけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15c",
      "text": " 配偶者",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15d",
      "text": " 友人",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15e",
      "text": "  リアルの友人",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc15f",
      "text": "  staさん()",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc160",
      "text": " 職場",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc161",
      "text": " 井戸端",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc162",
      "text": " エックス",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc163",
      "text": "  ここでは限られたものについてだけ情報源としてる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc164",
      "text": "   自ジャンルに関するもの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc165",
      "text": "   技術ネタ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc166",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776848749
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f6c00000000005bc167",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848749,
      "updated": 1776848749
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cafe",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776848791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085caff",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb00",
      "text": "最近の情報源",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb01",
      "text": " youtube",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb02",
      "text": " インスタ(ごはん系、イベント情報)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb03",
      "text": "  インスタはライブとか展示会情報を集めるのが容易な唯一の情報源な感じがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb04",
      "text": "  \t個人でやってる店の情報とかもインスタで得がち[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb05",
      "text": "  \t時間溶けるからインスタ禁止したいのに、インスタ見れないと生活できないの腹立つ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb06",
      "text": "  他だとそういう系のサイトをRSSでちゃんとチェックしないとだめそう？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb07",
      "text": " オタク情報は[X.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb08",
      "text": " ニュース系は[Feedly]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb09",
      "text": " 時事ネタ？は同僚、友人、井戸端に頼っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb0a",
      "text": " [Hiro Aki.icon]さんがよくラジオ情報源の話をしているのをみてラジオも面白そうだなと思っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb0b",
      "text": " \tひとまず[radiko]を試してみては[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776849438
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88f97000000000085cb0c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848791,
      "updated": 1776848791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d627",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776848833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d628",
      "text": "[カイト.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d629",
      "text": "主な情報源",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62a",
      "text": "\t[X]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62b",
      "text": "\t\t趣味全般",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62c",
      "text": "\t[YouTube]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62d",
      "text": "\t\t関心あること・趣味全般",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62e",
      "text": "\t[Feedly]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d62f",
      "text": "\t\tニュース全般",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d630",
      "text": "\tゲーム関連は上記に加えて、攻略サイト",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d631",
      "text": "\t\t特定のサイトに定めておらず、ゲームごとに違う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d632",
      "text": "\t[Google News]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d633",
      "text": " \t時事ネタ・地域ニュース",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d634",
      "text": "\t[友人]・[親族]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d635",
      "text": "  聞くより知ったことを発信していることが多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d636",
      "text": " 本",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d637",
      "text": "\t\t関心あること・趣味全般・技術関連",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d638",
      "text": "\t公式サイト",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d639",
      "text": "\t\t[コンサート・ライブ]、イベントに関しては・公式Xとともに必ず確認する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63a",
      "text": "\t[Cosense]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63b",
      "text": "\t[Gemini]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63c",
      "text": "\t\t[ハルシネーション]が起こっている前提で概要や気になることを確認",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63d",
      "text": "\t\t\t詳細は上記の情報源で補完",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63e",
      "text": "\t[ラジオ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d63f",
      "text": "\t\t[声優]・[Vtuber]のラジオしか聞かない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d640",
      "text": "\t\tパーソナリティ・ゲストの情報を聞くことはできる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776849436
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d641",
      "text": "基本的に一つの事に対して、色んな情報源から情報を取得することが多い",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776848833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d642",
      "text": "\tソース元を確認するクセが気づいたら着いていた",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776848833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fc10000000000d8d643",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848833,
      "updated": 1776848833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf43",
      "text": "from [2025/09/09]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776848871
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf44",
      "text": " [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849008
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf45",
      "text": " 主な情報源",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf46",
      "text": "  X / Twitter",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf47",
      "text": "  [Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf48",
      "text": "  　英語版のページを見ると日本ではあまり知られていない情報を拾えることもある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf49",
      "text": "  これくらいか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf4a",
      "text": "  　自分の[認知限界]により、大量に情報を受取ることは諦めた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e88fe700000000009aaf4b",
      "text": "  　\tme too[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848871,
      "updated": 1776849010
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890600000000000c51714",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848993,
      "updated": 1776849469
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890b60000000000c5171b",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849078,
      "updated": 1776849078
    },
    {
      "id": "69e892520000000000c51722",
      "text": "\t日記ページ由来ではない書き込み",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849491,
      "updated": 1776849505
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890670000000000c51715",
      "text": " 受動的な情報源は目に入ったニュース",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776848999,
      "updated": 1776849079
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890860000000000c51718",
      "text": " \tスマホのGoogleのトップに表示されるやつとか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849030,
      "updated": 1776849085
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890980000000000c51719",
      "text": "\t能動的に調べる時は主に Wikipedia",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849049,
      "updated": 1776849115
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890dc0000000000c5171c",
      "text": "\t\tどんな言語であってもも気にしない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849116,
      "updated": 1776849214
    },
    {
      "id": "69e890f40000000000c5171d",
      "text": "\t\t\tだから日本語英語以外の Wikiepdia を持ってくることがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849140,
      "updated": 1776849167
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8914d0000000000c5171f",
      "text": "\t\t\t日本語や英語よりも情報の質が良さげなことがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849229,
      "updated": 1776849248
    },
    {
      "id": "69e891610000000000c51720",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t例えば、A 国に関する話で A 語 以上に質の良い情報があるだろうか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849250,
      "updated": 1776849343
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8906a0000000000c51716",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776849002,
      "updated": 1776849002
    }
  ]
}